{"tid":1172723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我人生只去過兩次遊行，六月九號會係我第三次","createTime":"2019-05-26T15:29:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T16:24:08.000Z","uid":156659,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4287407b6d6860252a17574c78f4b1ec86dc7600","tid":1172723,"uid":156659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T15:29:40.000Z","msg":"第一次係2014年71<br />\n仲記得嗰日行出維園無耐就落大雨，仲要塞住係條街好耐<br />\n又濕又累咁行到中環，見住幾十萬人係街行真係好震憾<br />\n第二次係2016年反釋法<br />\n依次就比較少人，行完依次就變咗返工不了mode<br />\n六月九號會係我第三次行，上兩次行完都係失敗收場<br />\n我唔知今次行完係唔係都會係咁，但我決定要去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a81400bc00c3eee8b3eab0589e0d3490820d1a9","tid":1172723,"uid":199893,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T15:33:24.000Z","msg":"以前我年少無知，一個都冇去<br />\n今年6月9號，我必去<br />\n以此為證<br />\n----18歲學生"},{"pid":"cc048273473ba754a38d4ae4bed9b0480fa99841","tid":1172723,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9a81400bc00c3eee8b3eab0589e0d3490820d1a9","tid":1172723,"uid":199893,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T15:33:24.000Z","msg":"以前我年少無知，一個都冇去<br />\n今年6月9號，我必去<br />\n以此為證<br />\n----18歲學生"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T15:39:03.000Z","msg":"如果00<del>後</del>后多返你依啲人就好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3673f74c88966cdd741e3eb9c6a0893601b8b3cb","tid":1172723,"uid":199893,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"cc048273473ba754a38d4ae4bed9b0480fa99841","tid":1172723,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9a81400bc00c3eee8b3eab0589e0d3490820d1a9","tid":1172723,"uid":199893,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T15:33:24.000Z","msg":"以前我年少無知，一個都冇去<br />\n今年6月9號，我必去<br />\n以此為證<br />\n----18歲學生"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T15:39:03.000Z","msg":"如果00<del>後</del>后多返你依啲人就好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019